snippet.title: Beasts Of Prey Review (EA) - Worth a Buy?
snippet.description:
Early Access Review of Beasts of Prey - a new survival sandbox MMOFPS! Hunt Dinosaurs, craft items, build massive structures and create your own empire in a procedual generated game-world that grows with server population. - Is it worth a buy?
